<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>YelpCamp</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
</head>
<body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
    <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
        <header class="mb-auto">
            <div>
                <h3 class="float-md-start mb-0">YelpCamp</h3>
                <nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center float-md-end">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">홈페이지</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/campgrounds">모든 캠핑장들</a>
                    <% if(!currentUser) { %>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/login">로그인</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/register">등록하기</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
                    <% } %>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="px-3">
            <h1>YelpCamp</h1>
            <p class="lead"> YelpCamp에 오신 것을 환영합니다! <br> 우리의 다양한 캠핑장들을 둘러보세요. <br>
                자유롭게 새로운 캠핑장을 소개하고 리뷰도 남겨보세요!</p>
            <a href="/campgrounds" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary fw-bold bg-white">모든 캠핑장 보러가기</a>
        </main>

        <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
            <p>&copy; 2023 </p>
        </footer>


    </div>


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-IQsoLXl5PILFhosVNubq5LC7Qb9DXgDA9i+tQ8Zj3iwWAwPtgFTxbJ8NT4GN1R8p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-cVKIPhGWiC2Al4u+LWgxfKTRIcfu0JTxR+EQDz/bgldoEyl4H0zUF0QKbrJ0EcQF" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>